metadata.name: Lady Liberty
metadata.description: The September 11 attacks were a series of four coordinated terrorist attacks by the militant Islamist terrorist group al-Qaeda against the United States of America on the morning of Tuesday, September 11, 2001. "In remembrance of September 11th, let us never forget, our freedom is, and never will be, free." With this purchase the buyer will also receive a desktop holographic crystal and a 10" x 10" commemorative print.
